@startuml MyCPT_Sequence_Scoring

skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam defaultFontName "Apple SD Gothic Neo, sans-serif"
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam defaultFontColor #26215C
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

skinparam participant {
  BackgroundColor #FFFFFF
  BorderColor #AFA9EC
  FontColor #26215C
  FontSize 12
}

skinparam actor {
  BackgroundColor #FFFFFF
  BorderColor #7F77DD
  FontColor #3C3489
  FontSize 12
  FontStyle bold
}

skinparam sequence {
  ArrowColor #7F77DD
  ArrowFontColor #534AB7
  ArrowFontSize 10
  LifeLineBorderColor #AFA9EC
  LifeLineBackgroundColor #F5F3FF
  GroupBorderColor #534AB7
  GroupBackgroundColor #EEEDFE
  GroupFontColor #3C3489
  GroupFontSize 11
  GroupBodyBackgroundColor #F5F3FF
  DividerBackgroundColor #EEEDFE
  DividerBorderColor #534AB7
  DividerFontColor #3C3489
  ReferenceBackgroundColor #EEF6FF
  ReferenceBorderColor #534AB7
}

skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor #F5F3FF
  BorderColor #AFA9EC
  FontColor #534AB7
  FontSize 10
}

actor "사용자\n(비회원/회원)" as User
participant "Next.js" as Client
participant "ResultController" as Controller
participant "ScoringService" as Scoring
participant "CacheService" as CacheService
participant "LlmService" as Llm
database "Redis" as Redis
database "disc_cache\n(MySQL)" as DB

User -> Client : 24문항 응답 완료

Client -> Controller : POST /results/score\n{ testType, scores: { d, i, s, c } }
activate Controller

Controller -> Scoring : normalize(d, i, s, c)
activate Scoring

note right of Scoring
  D + I + S + C = 24 검증
  원점수 범위 검증 (-24~+48)
  원점수 → 버킷값 (1~3) 정규화
end note

Scoring -> Scoring : 버킷값 정규화\n(원점수 -24~+48 → 3단계)
Scoring --> Controller : { d, i, s, c 원점수 + 버킷값 }
deactivate Scoring

Controller -> CacheService : getReport(d, i, s, c 버킷값)
activate CacheService

CacheService -> Redis : GET disc_cache:{d}:{i}:{s}:{c}
activate Redis

alt Redis 캐시 HIT
  Redis --> CacheService : 캐시 데이터 반환
  deactivate Redis
  CacheService --> Controller : 보고서 반환
  note right of CacheService : Redis HIT → DB 조회 생략

else Redis 캐시 MISS
  Redis --> CacheService : null
  deactivate Redis

  CacheService -> DB : SELECT WHERE d=? AND i=? AND s=? AND c=?
  activate DB

  alt 캐시 HIT + 유효 (created_at >= 만료 기준)
    DB --> CacheService : 캐시 행 반환
    deactivate DB
    CacheService -> Redis : SET disc_cache:{d}:{i}:{s}:{c}
    CacheService --> Controller : 보고서 반환

  else 캐시 HIT + 만료 (created_at < 만료 기준)
    DB --> CacheService : 만료된 캐시 행 반환
    deactivate DB
    CacheService -> Llm : generateReport(버킷값)
    activate Llm
    Llm -> Llm : 프롬프트 구성\n(6개 섹션 요청)
    Llm --> CacheService : Markdown 보고서
    deactivate Llm
    CacheService -> DB : UPDATE SET report=?, created_at=NOW()\nWHERE d=? AND i=? AND s=? AND c=?
    note right of DB : 행 DELETE 없이 UPDATE\nFK 참조 무결성 유지
    CacheService -> Redis : SET disc_cache:{d}:{i}:{s}:{c}
    CacheService --> Controller : 보고서 반환

  else 캐시 MISS (행 없음)
    CacheService -> Llm : generateReport(버킷값)
    activate Llm
    Llm -> Llm : 프롬프트 구성\n(6개 섹션 요청)
    Llm --> CacheService : Markdown 보고서
    deactivate Llm
    CacheService -> DB : INSERT (d, i, s, c, report, created_at)
    CacheService -> Redis : SET disc_cache:{d}:{i}:{s}:{c}
    CacheService --> Controller : 보고서 반환
  end

end

deactivate CacheService

Controller --> Client : 200 OK\n{ rawScores, buckets, report }
deactivate Controller

alt 비회원
  Client -> Client : sessionStorage에\nDISC 원점수 저장
  note right of Client
    서버 세션 미발급
    (플러딩 방어)
  end note
end

Client --> User : 결과 화면 표시\n(보고서 렌더링 시 이름 삽입)

@enduml